article.description: — Jahmir Young had 18 points and seven rebounds as Charlotte beat Davidson 63-52 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Young, Shepherd carry Charlotte over Davidson 63-52
article.linkText: Young, Shepherd carry Charlotte over Davidson 63-52
article.story: DAVIDSON, N.C. -- — Jahmir Young had 18 points and seven rebounds as Charlotte beat Davidson 63-52 on Tuesday night. Jordan Shepherd added 16 points and seven rebounds for the 49ers (2-3). Milos Supica chipped in 11 points. Kellan Grady had 23 points and seven rebounds for the Wildcats (3-3). Hyunjung Lee added 16 points and seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
